OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784751301
OL,3,CCamden born N-Dubz singer Tulisa calls
OL,4,Cfor 'fairness and truth' in UK media
OL,6,FThe charges against the 38 year old
OL,7,Fwere dismissed in 2014 after
OL,8,Fprosecution witness and "Fake Sheikh"
OL,9,Fjournalist Mazher Mahmood was found
OL,10,Fguilty of tampering with evidence.
OL,12,FHe was jailed for 15 months in 2016.
OL,14,FContostavlos says her new campaign
OL,15,Fhopes to "give some meaning and
OL,16,Fpurpose behind all the chaos" that
OL,17,Fleft her reputation in tatters. She
OL,18,Fsaid:
OL,26,@pD@YOUpD@eO]wD@JOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784751301
OL,3,CCamden born N-Dubz singer Tulisa calls
OL,4,Cfor 'fairness and truth' in UK media
OL,6,F"I'm in quite a healed place at the
OL,7,Fmoment, which is why I'm able to do
OL,8,Fsomething like this and start this
OL,9,Fcampaign.
OL,11,F"I don't understand why there's such a
OL,12,Fbig fear around simple regulation.
OL,14,F"All I ask for is fairness and the
OL,15,Ftruth."
OL,17,FContostavlos is advocating for a truly
OL,18,Findependent media regulator which the
OL,19,Fpress does not control, fund or
OL,20,Fappoint, and has the power to
OL,21,F"investigate, fine and protect people".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@GO]}D@AOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
