OL,3,CCamden born N-Dubz singer Tulisa calls
OL,4,Cfor 'fairness and truth' in UK media
OL,6,FThe star spoke about the Independent
OL,7,FPress Standards Organisation.
OL,9,FThis is the independent regulator for
OL,10,Fthe majority of UK's newspaper and
OL,11,Fmagazine industry. It's funded by
OL,12,Fmember publications. Contostavlos said:
OL,14,F"Ipso isn't independent of the press,
OL,15,Fbecause it is funded and run by the
OL,16,Fpress itself.
OL,18,F"The press are essentially regulating
OL,19,Fthemselves. It's really coming down to
OL,20,Fethics."
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
