CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784751301
OL,3,CCamden born N-Dubz singer Tulisa calls
OL,4,Cfor 'fairness and truth' in UK media
OL,6,FThe former X Factor judge also claimed
OL,7,Fthat the press has "unlimited power",
OL,8,Fand added that it "is one of the
OL,9,Fbiggest corporations in the world."
OL,11,FContostavlos has joined the mother of
OL,12,Fthe late Caroline Flack, as well as
OL,13,FHillsborough campaigners Margaret
OL,14,FAspinall and Sue Roberts, in demanding
OL,15,Faction against press abuse.
OL,26,@oD@TOUoD@dO]pD@SOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
