OL,3,CCamden born N-Dubz singer Tulisa calls
OL,4,Cfor 'fairness and truth' in UK media
OL,6,FIn 2011 she became a judge on popular
OL,7,Freality singing series The X Factor
OL,8,Fwhere she helped girl group Little Mix
OL,9,Fwin, and a year later she released her
OL,10,Fdebut solo album, The Female Boss.
OL,12,FThe Camden-born star has released two
OL,13,Fautobiographies, and her 2025 memoir
OL,14,FJudgement details the highs and
OL,15,F"unimaginable lows" of her music
OL,16,Fcareer, including her collapsed drugs
OL,17,Ftrial.
OL,19,FThe Sun has been contacted for comment.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@SO]
